00:22:09,060 --> 00:22:12,060
And what about this little fishcake?
- Don't touch her!

261
00:22:13,145 --> 00:22:15,145
Are you going to abandon her?

262
00:22:15,826 --> 00:22:20,053
Shall Herr Heydrich play
with her after school?

263
00:22:20,773 --> 00:22:22,106
Don't touch her!

264
00:22:23,773 --> 00:22:25,333
I could.

265
00:22:25,976 --> 00:22:28,320
Then she'll finally get a real man.

266
00:22:28,373 --> 00:22:29,413
Now it's over.

267
00:22:29,500 --> 00:22:32,406
I'm not letting myself
get walked over! Darn it!

268
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:39,566
Sorry.

269
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:59,060
Barteljaap! Barteljaap! Barteljaap!
Barteljaap! Barteljaap! Barteljaap!

